172033838.html">最佳游戏笔记本电脑</a>指南中将其作为首选推荐。此配置是 2022 年型号 - <a data-i13n="cpos:45;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/razer-updates-the-blade-15-with-13th-gen-intel-cpus-and-rtx-40-series-graphics-190544878.html">最新版本</a>主要是规格提升 - 但它仍然足够强大，可以在高设置和帧速率下玩大多数现代游戏，尤其是使用 DLSS 时。不过，为任何刀片笔记本电脑支付高价的主要原因是因为它采用纤薄且具有优质感觉的铝制设计来提供强大的功能。请注意，它可能会很热，并且电池寿命相当短。</p><h2>三星M80B智能显示器（32英寸） </h2><p><core-commerce id="dddaaac0c1b740ff92c248c54fac0abe" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>大量<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:46;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kZWFsL2UyNzA1ZTY5P3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFwbS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMmUwYjg1YzQtZDU2Yi00Nzc1LTkyNGItNmIyY2U1MzBhNzExIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAfPxset55015oBODS1bZb766rO9E69aJc-CvKqMlnS6g&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdeal%2Fe2705e69" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/deal/e2705e69?showVariations=true&amp;pf_rd_r=XZRD6S0MFJXWGFD3194E&amp;pf_rd_t=Events&amp;pf_rd_i=deals&amp;pf_rd_p=ce138ca9-6c46-40eb-895a-87cea6cb67e3&amp;pf_rd_s=slot-14" class="rapid-with-clickid">三星显示器</a>正在促销，其中包括售价 400 美元的<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:47;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASaCmo4KfCn3F7kDB2UXs-KTHgGXzdbNksrT5Xbt6leN&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSAMSUNG-Computer-Streaming-Included-LS32BM805UNXGO%2Fdp%2FB0B89L2WNV" class="rapid-with-clickid">Smart Monitor M80B</a> 。这虽然不像 Prime Day 的 380 美元那么低，但仍然节省了近 100 美元。 32 英寸显示屏具有显示器、智能电视和智能家居中心的三重功能。您可以像任何其他外部